data.description: Located in the Blue Ridge Mountains of Western, NC you will find this executive dream home located in the desirable Mystic Cove subdivision only a quick 15 min drive to Asheville and 15 min to Waynesville.  In this genuinely friendly neighborhood, you will likely be invited to enjoy a late afternoon aperitif and cookout as you gather with kind neighbors.  This expansive home offers an unusual three full bedrooms on the main level including a primary suite, two full baths, vaulted ceiling in living room with fireplace, custom kitchen, dining area, two car garage and laundry room. The fully finished basement is sure to WOW you, with a gigantic living area, wet bar, gym/recreation area.  There is also an additional sleeping quarters in the basement providing 4 possible spaces which family members can use as private retreats and a full bathroom. House is on a three bedroom septic.
